OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775300571
OL,3,CThree teenagers in court over murder
OL,4,Cof Chloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FThree teenagers have appeared at Leeds
OL,7,FCrown Court charged with the murder of
OL,8,FChloe Watson Dransfield.
OL,10,FChloe was found unconscious at an
OL,11,Faddress on Kennerleigh Avenue in
OL,12,FAusthorpe in the early hours of
OL,13,FSaturday 28 March.
OL,15,FShe died in hospital a short time
OL,16,Flater.
OL,18,FOn Thursday 2 April three teenagers
OL,19,Fappeared at Leeds Crown Court via
OL,20,Fvideo link from a secure accommodation
OL,21,Funit.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
