PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775300571
OL,3,CThree teenagers in court over murder
OL,4,Cof Chloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FKayla Smith, aged 18 and of
OL,7,FKennerleigh Avenue, and Archie
OL,8,FRycroft, aged 19 and of Middleton Park
OL,9,FRoad, are both charged with murder.
OL,11,FA 17-year-old boy who cannot be named
OL,12,Fbecause of his age has also been
OL,13,Fcharged with murder. West Yorkshire
OL,14,FPolice confirmed all three self-
OL,15,Fdefined as white British.
OL,17,FAll three spoke only to confirm their
OL,18,Fnames and dates of birth during the 12-
OL,19,Fminute hearing.
OL,21,FNo applications for bail were made.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
