CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775300571
OL,3,CThree teenagers in court over murder
OL,4,Cof Chloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FRecorder of Leeds, Judge Guy Kearl KC,
OL,7,Fsaid a pre-trial hearing will take
OL,8,Fplace 1 May where pleas will be
OL,9,Fentered.
OL,11,FA provisional trial date was also set
OL,12,Ffor 10 November, which is expected to
OL,13,Flast more than two weeks.
OL,15,FHe said: "It's important that this
OL,16,Fmatter is dealt with as soon as
OL,17,Fpossibly can be ` any delay should be
OL,18,Fkept to a minimum."
OL,26,@wD@JOUzD@SO]
