OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775300571
OL,3,CThree teenagers in court over murder
OL,4,Cof Chloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FThe court was also told a second post-
OL,7,Fmortem examination for the victim was
OL,8,Fnot required, which would be a comfort
OL,9,Fto her family.
OL,11,FAll three were remanded in custody
OL,12,Funtil the next hearing.
